== 游戏玩法 ==
尽管本作不是一款网络游戏，但仍引入许多[[大型多人在线角色扮演游戏|大型多人在线角色扮演游戏]]中的元素。其中包括购买和升级武器，执行任务，以及和其他一些角色组团进行战斗。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/sword-art-online-infinity-moment-is-tailor-made-for-fa-470822066|title=''Sword Art Online: Infinity Moment'' is Tailor-Made for Fans of the Franchise|publisher=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|language=en|date=2013-04-05|accessdate=2014-06-10|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304031024/http://kotaku.com/sword-art-online-infinity-moment-is-tailor-made-for-fa-470822066|dead-url=no}}</ref>主角桐人可以装备包括剑和斧在内的十种武器。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.siliconera.com/2012/12/27/kirito-has-10-different-weapons-in-sword-art-online-infinity-moment/|title=Kirito Has 10 Different Weapons In Sword Art Online: Infinity Moment|publisher=Siliconera|language=en|date=2012-12-07|accessdate=2018-04-14|archive-date=2019-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190114171745/http://www.siliconera.com/2012/12/27/kirito-has-10-different-weapons-in-sword-art-online-infinity-moment/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
== 剧情 ==
原作艾恩葛朗特篇剧情中，桐人在75层打败了希兹克利夫（茅场晶彦）迎来了终局。但在游戏中，桐人打败了希兹克利夫后仍未脱离游戏世界。玩家要扮演桐人，从76层开始，和同伴们一起在系统崩坏之前攻下第100层。
== 开发 ==
万代南梦宫于2014年6月释出本作的升级补丁，在游戏二周目中追加困难模式。<ref name="Patch">{{cite web|title=Sword Art Online: Infinity Moment Tops 200,000 Units Shipped And Adds New Patch|url=http://www.siliconera.com/2013/06/07/sword-art-online-infinity-moment-tops-200000-units-shipped-and-adds-new-patch/|publisher=Siliconera|language=en|date=2013-06-07|accessdate=2018-04-14|archive-date=2015-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151122061923/http://www.siliconera.com/2013/06/07/sword-art-online-infinity-moment-tops-200000-units-shipped-and-adds-new-patch/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 评价 ==
游戏在日本第一周共售出13.8万份实体版，成为日本该周销量第一软件。<ref>{{cite web|title=This Week In Sales: Kingdom Hearts HD Falls To Sword Art Online|url=http://www.siliconera.com/2013/03/20/this-week-in-sales-kingdom-hearts-hd-falls-to-sword-art-online/|publisher=Siliconera|language=en|date=2013-03-20|accessdate=2018-04-14|archive-date=2015-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151122061919/http://www.siliconera.com/2013/03/20/this-week-in-sales-kingdom-hearts-hd-falls-to-sword-art-online/|dead-url=no}}</ref>至2013年6月，出货量已达20万份。<ref name="Patch" />[[Fami通|Fami通]]给予本作8/7/7/7 [29/40]的评分。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gematsu.com/2013/03/famitsu-review-scores-issue-1264|title=Famitsu Review Scores: Issue 1264|publisher=Gematsu|date=2013-03-05|accessdate=2018-04-14|archive-date=2020-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200815171238/https://www.gematsu.com/2013/03/famitsu-review-scores-issue-1264|dead-url=no}}</ref>
